    "Then, the functional E(f) controls the relaxation of these collisional equilibria toward distributions of Ker (L EL + L CH), which are chemical local equilibria whose n i (t, x) are now linked together with e(t, x) by the additional relation (31) imposed by the mass action law (21).",
